<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | SchoolFlow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --dark: #0f172a;
            --text-slate: #475569;
            --bg-light: #f8fafc;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .about-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .about-hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Content Section */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: -50px auto 80px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .story-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .story-text h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .story-text p {
            color: var(--text-slate);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Mission & Vision Grid */
        .vision-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .vision-item {
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .vision-item i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .vision-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-box h4 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .stat-box p {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-slate);
        }

        /* Responsive Fixes */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .story-card { padding: 30px; }
            .container { margin-top: -30px; }
            .about-hero { padding: 80px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include("partials/HomePageNavbar") %>

    <section class="about-hero">
        <h1>Transforming Education</h1>
        <p>Empowering schools with smart technology to focus more on teaching and less on paperwork.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-text">
                <h2>The SchoolFlow Journey</h2>
                <p>
                    SchoolFlow was born out of a simple idea: <strong>Why should school management be complicated?</strong> 
                    In a world where everything is just a click away, we realized that many educational institutions 
                    still struggle with manual attendance, messy fee records, and communication gaps.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Founded by <strong>Harshita Garg</strong>, SchoolFlow is designed to be the backbone of modern schools. 
                    We don't just provide a software; we provide a system that brings transparency, efficiency, 
                    and ease to students, parents, and administrators alike.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="vision-grid">
                <div class="vision-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i>
                    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>To digitize every school in India by providing affordable, high-end management tools that simplify daily operations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="vision-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>
                    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                    <p>Building an ecosystem where data-driven insights help educators improve student outcomes and institutional growth.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h4>100%</h4>
                    <p>Secure Data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h4>24/7</h4>
                    <p>Fast Support</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h4>Smart</h4>
                    <p>Fee Payments</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/HomePageFooter") %>
<script src="/backButton.js"></script>
</body>
</html>